  "title": "Warehouse Assistant cum Delivery Driver (Class 3/Class 4) #77092",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing (Food Ingredients)</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Warehouse Assistant cum Delivery Driver (Class 3/Class 4)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Bishan</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (8.30AM – 5PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $2,400 + AWS + Bonus + OT</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Receive, check, and organize incoming goods; assist with unloading and proper storage in the warehouse.</li><li>Pick, pack, and prepare orders accurately for delivery or collection according to company procedures.</li><li>Conduct regular stock checks, update inventory records, and report any discrepancies to supervisors.</li><li>Load goods onto delivery vehicle, plan efficient delivery routes, and deliver items to customers in a timely and safe manner.</li><li>Ensure all delivery and warehouse records, including delivery orders and receipts, are completed accurately and maintained properly.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and orderliness of the warehouse and delivery vehicle at all times.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Proficient in using computers for data entries in Microsoft Excel, Word, and labelling software.</li><li>With a valid Class 3/Class 4 Driving License</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77092 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
